The paper deals with the Facility Location problem on planar graphs, which involves both graph theory and optimization. Therefore, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are all likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves approximation algorithms, which falls under cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
